short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension filters the search results to only show locations with open appointments.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Installing this extension allows users on the OSDH Vaccine Portal to change the location map results to only show locations that have open appointments.
